  "original_title": "ICTA \u0db1\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba \u0db8\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dab\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "ICTA new president Professor Malik Ranasinghe",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the new chairman of the Information and Communication Technology Agency (ICTA), Professor Malik Ranasinghe started his duties in that position recently.",
        "Professor Malik Ranasinghe is a Senior Professor of Civil Engineering at the University of Moratuwa. He is a chartered, international professional engineer and a member of the Sri Lanka Institute of Engineering. He is also a member of the Sri Lanka National Academy of Sciences, a graduate member of the Institute of Project Managers of Sri Lanka and the Institute of Directors of Sri Lanka.",
        "A former Vice-Chancellor of the University of Moratuwa, Professor Ranasinghe is also a former member of the National University of Singapore, and a former Commission Member of the University Grants Commission. Former Council Member of National Research Council and Association of Commonwealth Universities."
      ],
